{CritterProperty::ModJoeVampire}{1}{Modoc needs your help again. According to Joe, something is wrong with the livestock. Find Grisham, he'll fill you in on the details.}
{CritterProperty::ModJoeVampire}{2}{Old Grisham is worried about the condition of the brahmin. Head to the farm and find out what's going on.}
