{CritterProperty::ModJoeVampire}{4}{Heh. This thing is afraid of people. You just need to post a guard.}
{CritterProperty::ModJoeVampire}{5}{"It" flew off somewhere north of Modoc. You could try searching the area.}
{CritterProperty::ModJoeVampire}{6}{You found a strange cave. It looks like someone lives there. Or something.}
{CritterProperty::ModJoeVampire}{7}{Emil didn't live to see your help. You were too late.}
{CritterProperty::ModJoeVampire}{8}{You killed the man (or not-man?) who called himself Emil Regis. Good or bad, it doesn't matter. At least the brahmin will be safe!}
{CritterProperty::ModJoeVampire}{9}{You cured Emil Regis's affliction. The farm is safe. Return to Grisham.}
{CritterProperty::ModJoeVampire}{10}{You solved the problem of the Modoc farmers. Nothing threatens the brahmin anymore.}
{CritterProperty::ModJoeVampire}{11}{Good deeds pay off. You saved a vampire and gained a new ability. Only your neck aches and itches for some reason…}

