# Город-убежище,Хартманн
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{1}{You must take part in patrolling the outskirts of Vault City. Find Corporal Shrim in the Outer City near the barracks.}
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{2}{You're part of a guardsmen patrol squad. The patrol has begun.}
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{3}{Failure: you tried to rob or attacked the patrolmen.}
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{4}{Failure: you abandoned the patrol squad without permission.}
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{5}{You died while carrying out Corporal Shrim's task.}
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{6}{Corporal Shrim died on the mission. }
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{7}{Failure: You finished off Corporal Shrim. Better not show yourself to him.}
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{8}{Task complete. Go to Captain Hartmann for your reward. And hurry, he won't wait long.}
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{9}{Another patrol. Good luck!}
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{10}{Another patrol finished. Go to the captain for your reward.}
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{11}{You successfully completed the captain's task and received your reward. Come back in 2 days.}

{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{QName}{Vault City}
{CritterProperty::VCShrimPatrol}{QDesc}{An easy stroll}
#==================================================================================================#
# Город-убежище, Хартманн
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannRecon}{1}{You must confirm or refute the rumors of a gathering of supermutants on the outskirts of Vault City.}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannRecon}{2}{You found the lair of the supermutant bandits. You need to report this to Hartmann immediately.}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannRecon}{3}{Failure! You gave yourself away. Now the supermutants will leave their hideout and no one will find them.}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannRecon}{4}{You handled the assigned task brilliantly. Captain Hartmann's suspicions were confirmed. Hostile supermutants have been found in the outskirts of Vault City.}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannRecon}{5}{You failed the recon mission. The supermutants noticed your appearance. Now they must be searched for elsewhere.}

{CritterProperty::VCHartmannRecon}{QName}{Vault City}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannRecon}{QDesc}{Go there - I know not where.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Город-убежище, Хартманн
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannClearCave}{1}{With the help of several guardsmen, destroy the supermutant lair. No one must escape alive. The guardsmen will wait at the entrance to the lair.}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannClearCave}{2}{The supermutant lair is destroyed. Report your success to Hartmann.}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannClearCave}{3}{You took too long to reach the lair. The mutants managed to flee their position}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannClearCave}{4}{You handled the assigned task brilliantly. Captain Hartmann's suspicions were confirmed. Hostile supermutants have been found in the outskirts of Vault City.}

{CritterProperty::VCHartmannClearCave}{QName}{Vault City}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmannClearCave}{QDesc}{A dangerous hunt.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Город-убежище, Хартманн
{CritterProperty::VCHartmanNcrHelp}{1}{Recent events tied to the increased mutant activity have led to Vault City needing help from outside forces. You must reach General Sheyman in the NCR and secure his support.}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmanNcrHelp}{2}{General Sheyman listened to you and is convening the NCR Council to make a decision. Return to Army Headquarters in a day.}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmanNcrHelp}{3}{Only thanks to your innate gift for eloquence were you able to convince General Sheyman to support Vault City in this difficult time. Return to Captain Hartmann.}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmanNcrHelp}{4}{You helped Vault City gain the support of the NCR Army and General Sheyman personally.}

{CritterProperty::VCHartmanNcrHelp}{QName}{Vault City}
{CritterProperty::VCHartmanNcrHelp}{QDesc}{Diplomatic courier}
#==================================================================================================#
# Город-убежище, Аманда
{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{1}{Amanda's husband, Joshua, was sentenced to several years of corrective labor for a minor offense. This is unjust. Help Joshua's family deal with this problem.}
{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{2}{You agreed to help Amanda and free her husband in exchange for a "small favor". Ethical or not, who cares? She didn't resist too long, anyway. Talk to Barkus, at the Servant Allocation Center, to find out how Joshua can be freed.}
{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{3}{You convinced Barkus that Joshua is your personal servant. Now you need to find 1234 coins to cover the Servant Allocation Center's expenses, and Joshua will be free.}
{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{4}{You paid for Joshua. He can return home.}
{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{5}{It's good to be a Citizen! All problems are solved in the blink of an eye. Joshua is free, return to Amanda with the joyful news.}
{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{6}{You helped Amanda free Joshua from the Servant Allocation Center.}
{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{7}{The problem seems solved, but at what cost? You need to tell Amanda and get out of Vault City.}
{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{8}{The problem seems solved, but at what cost? That dog Barkus awaits your visit. You need to tell Amanda and get out of Vault City.}
{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{9}{You helped Amanda settle Joshua's problem. The family is happy, but now the lecherous Servant Coordinator is waiting for you. Better not show yourself to him.}

{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{QName}{Vault City}
{CritterProperty::VCAmandaHelpJoshua}{QDesc}{An "amnesty" for Joshua.}
