{CritterProperty::VCLynettScareNewcomers}{1}{You received a task from Lynette. The newcomers must be made to keep quiet.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettScareNewcomers}{2}{You put the first newcomer in his place.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettScareNewcomers}{3}{You put the second newcomer in his place.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettScareNewcomers}{4}{You whipped three newcomers into line. Return to Lynette.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettScareNewcomers}{5}{You silenced the malcontents. The newcomers now keep quiet and look at the ground.}

{CritterProperty::VCLynettScareNewcomers}{QName}{Vault City}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettScareNewcomers}{QDesc}{Wrath.}
