# Город-убежище, Линетт
{CritterProperty::VCLynettArest}{1}{On the orders of the First Citizen, arrest one of McClure's supporters. The pretext - suspicion of high treason.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettArest}{2}{No one promised it would be easy. Knock some sense into the offender, and arrest him.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettArest}{3}{You got the upper hand over McClure's supporter. Take him to prison.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettArest}{4}{Task complete. The traitor is arrested. Guilty or not, that's a secondary question.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettArest}{5}{You arrested one of }

{CritterProperty::VCLynettArest}{QName}{Vault City}
