{CritterProperty::VCLynettForgery}{1}{On the orders of the First Citizen, plant incriminating documents on McClure.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettForgery}{2}{The plant failed. Leave the premises.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettForgery}{3}{You completed Lynette's task. The incriminating evidence is in one of the drawers in McClure's private house.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettForgery}{4}{You must find the incriminating documents in front of witnesses. Go to the councilor and conduct a search with witnesses present.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettForgery}{5}{The councilor is compromised. Some might say it's all conjecture. But the witnesses won't keep quiet.}
{CritterProperty::VCLynettForgery}{6}{Thanks to you, Lynette is now on top. One can definitely say your conscience is made of rubber.}

