# Караван Брокен-Хиллс - Гекко
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{1}{You signed up to guard Christopher Carson's caravan from Broken Hills, heading to Gecko. You need to be near him at 10:00, or the caravan will leave without you.}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{2}{You're part of the caravan. The task is to escort the caravan to its destination.}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{3}{You attacked Christopher Carson's caravan, heading from Broken Hills to Gecko. Kit will probably never hire you to guard his cargo.}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{4}{Failure: You abandoned the Broken Hills caravan in the Wasteland. You won't get a reward.}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{5}{Failure: You failed the caravan guarding tasks. You died during the route.}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{6}{Failure: Carson died in the Wasteland. You couldn't protect the caravan master.}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{7}{You killed the guide of the Broken Hills - Gecko caravan. Christopher Carson is unlikely to want to deal with you.}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{8}{Magnificent! The caravan safely reached its destination. Collect your pay from Bill Outfit in Broken Hills.}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{9}{You're part of the caravan. Try to keep the cargo safe and protect the guide throughout the entire route.}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{10}{Another success! The caravan is at its destination. Ben Wade will appreciate your work.}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{11}{You completed the task of escorting and guarding the caravan to Gecko.}

{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{QName}{Broken Hills}
{CritterProperty::BHKitCaravanEscort}{QDesc}{Guarding the Broken Hills - Gecko caravan}
