{CritterProperty::BHSuperNewTechnology}{2}{Kill 40 saboteurs in the outskirts of San Francisco.}
{CritterProperty::BHSuperNewTechnology}{3}{You completed the Hubologists' task. You need to return to AHS-7.}
{CritterProperty::BHSuperNewTechnology}{4}{You received a disk with a description of the uranium enrichment technology. Take it to the Broken Hills enrichment plant.}
{CritterProperty::BHSuperNewTechnology}{5}{You breathed new life into the Broken Hills enrichment plant. The ghouls are deadly grateful to you.}

{CritterProperty::BHSuperNewTechnology}{QName}{Broken Hills}
