# Квест "Кошачья Лапка."
{CritterProperty::BHMarcusEscort}{1}{At Marcus's request, bring one of the pretty girls from the "Cat's Paw" to Broken Hills.}
{CritterProperty::BHMarcusEscort}{2}{One of the "Cat's Paw" prostitutes agreed to visit Marcus. Escort the girl to Broken Hills.}
{CritterProperty::BHMarcusEscort}{3}{Despite all the difficulties and dangers lurking at every step, you brought the prostitute from New Reno to Marcus. Return to Marcus in a day.}
{CritterProperty::BHMarcusEscort}{4}{You fulfilled Marcus's request and brought him a professional from the "Cat's Paw".}
{CritterProperty::BHMarcusEscort}{5}{You sold Marcus out completely to Zaius. Marcus is unlikely to talk to you after this.}

{CritterProperty::BHMarcusEscort}{QName}{Broken Hills}
{CritterProperty::BHMarcusEscort}{QDesc}{Cat's Paw.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Квест "Рискованное дельце."
{CritterProperty::BHRocketBase}{1}{Mickey from Broken Hills told you about a suspicious guy in the bar who is looking for a reliable man. The job, according to Mickey, is lucrative.}
{CritterProperty::BHRocketBase}{2}{You met with Tuco in the Broken Hills bar. Tuco offered you to take part in a looting raid on an abandoned military facility. The meeting place with Tuco's accomplices is marked on your map.}
{CritterProperty::BHRocketBase}{3}{Damn it! Tuco betrayed you and lured you into a trap! The drifters are trying to kill you.}
{CritterProperty::BHRocketBase}{4}{Despite Tuco's betrayal, the sortie was a success. You have the coordinates of the military facility that crook spoke of.}
{CritterProperty::BHRocketBase}{5}{You entered the territory of the abandoned military facility.}

{CritterProperty::BHRocketBase}{QName}{Broken Hills}
{CritterProperty::BHRocketBase}{QDesc}{A risky little deal.}
