#========================================== Нью-Рено ==============================================#
#==================================================================================================#
# Проблемы мистера Райта: Заложник.
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{1}{Oliver Wright's son is held captive by a gang of raiders. Free the hostage and deal with the bandits.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{2}{You paid the raiders the ransom. Tell Wright's son that he is free.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{3}{You killed the raider who was guarding Wright's son. Get out of here quick, before the gang notices your presence.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{4}{Don't make any sudden moves. Carefully, without provocation, help Wright leave the raiders' lair.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{5}{Wright's son is saved. With minimal losses you freed the hostage. The bandits remained alive. Tell Orville Wright about everything that happened.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{6}{Wright's son is saved. The gang of raiders is destroyed. Return to New Reno to receive your well-earned reward.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{7}{Circumstances did not turn out in your favor. Wright's son is dead, the raiders suffered no significant losses. Orville Wright must learn what happened here.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{8}{Even though Wright's son perished, you carried out Orville's assignment. The raiders are destroyed. Return to New Reno and tell Orville Wright what happened.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{9}{You freed the hostage, but did not deal with the bandits. Orville Wright's assignment is only half complete.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{10}{You failed Orville Wright's task. His son perished, and his death went unavenged.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{11}{You managed to save the hostage and dealt with the raiders. This had a favorable effect on your relations with the Wright family.}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{12}{You avenged the raiders for Wright's death and reported the son's demise to Orville.}

{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{QName}{New Reno}
{CritterProperty::NRWriKidnap}{QDesc}{Mr. Wright's problems: The Hostage.}
