{CritterProperty::NRBarmenEscort}{2}{The bartender's family has given their consent. Now talk to Topler himself.}
{CritterProperty::NRBarmenEscort}{3}{Escort Topler Harvey to his new place of work.}
{CritterProperty::NRBarmenEscort}{4}{You safely avoided all the dangers of the Wasteland and escorted Topler Harvey to his new bar. Now your city has an excellent bartender!}

