{CritterProperty::NcrLeadSmit2Dustybar}{2}{The customs captain agreed to look the other way on Smith. You can bring him in without the usual paperwork procedure.}
{CritterProperty::NcrLeadSmit2Dustybar}{3}{The guards at the city entrance let Smith through. Find your new buddy in the center of town, at Dusty's bar.}
{CritterProperty::NcrLeadSmit2Dustybar}{4}{You helped Smith get into the NCR without a pass. Wonder what all the secrecy is about?}

