{CritterProperty::NcrDappoLostC}{3}{Dappo asked you to find the caravan carrying Buster's cargo. The caravan was last seen near Vault 15.}
{CritterProperty::NcrDappoLostC}{4}{The remains of the caravan have been found. The crate being delivered to Buster held a combat robot. For some reason it activated and killed all the caravan drivers. You can return to Dappo.}
