{CritterProperty::NcrRatchBuggy}{1}{Ratch claims he can build a buggy. You need to bring Ratch super tools, a motor, an oil can and 10,000 coins.}
{CritterProperty::NcrRatchBuggy}{2}{Everything needed to build the buggy has been gathered, including the 10,000 payment. But Ratch needs the blueprints for the buggy's engine suspension. The schematic can be found in the Sierra computer network.}
{CritterProperty::NcrRatchBuggy}{3}{One of the mechanics who served at Sierra left the technical specs of his buggy on a computer at the military base. The data has been saved to a holodisk. Return to Ratch."}
