{CritterProperty::NcrRatchBuggy}{5}{Ratch has started building the buggy. Come back to see him in a week.}
{CritterProperty::NcrRatchBuggy}{6}{Amazing, but Ratch really can make something that works out of a pile of junk. Your brand-new buggy is perfect proof of that!}

