# Дипломатическая миссия - обмен нотами протеста между НКР и братством стали
{CritterProperty::NcrShaimanProtest}{1}{On orders from Victor Shaiman, commander of the NCR Army, you must deliver the NCR's protest against the Brotherhood of Steel's expansion into Northern California. Head to the Brotherhood outpost in San Francisco.}
{CritterProperty::NcrShaimanProtest}{2}{You delivered the protest to the Brotherhood of Steel paladins.}
{CritterProperty::NcrShaimanProtest}{3}{You delivered the protest to the Brotherhood of Steel paladins. Wait while the paladins draft a reply.}
{CritterProperty::NcrShaimanProtest}{4}{You have a case with the Brotherhood of Steel's official reply to General Shaiman's protest. Deliver the case to the commander.}
{CritterProperty::NcrShaimanProtest}{5}{You opened the case with the Brotherhood's official reply! Better not tell anyone about it and throw the case away.}
{CritterProperty::NcrShaimanProtest}{6}{Shaiman's mission is complete. You delivered the protest to the Brotherhood of Steel paladins and brought the Brotherhood's official reply back to Shaiman.}
{CritterProperty::NcrShaimanProtest}{7}{You delivered the protest note to the Brotherhood of Steel, but couldn't get a reply from them. Mission failed.}

{CritterProperty::NcrShaimanProtest}{QName}{NCR}
{CritterProperty::NcrShaimanProtest}{QDesc}{Diplomatic Mission}
