{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagoSpyMission}{1}{On orders from Santiago, head of the NCR Counterintelligence Agency, infiltrate Vault City and record Councilor Lynette's report on tape. Try not to get detected.}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagoSpyMission}{17}{You have begun recording Councilor McClure's report. Be extremely careful! }
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagoSpyMission}{18}{You were exposed while carrying out the task. Mission failed.}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagoSpyMission}{19}{You didn't hear McClure's report all the way through. Mission failed.}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagoSpyMission}{20}{You recorded Councilor McClure's entire report. Return to Santiago!}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagoSpyMission}{21}{You completed Santiago's task.}

{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagoSpyMission}{QName}{NCR}
