#==================================================================================================#
# Найти шпиона для Сантьяго
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagaFindSpyStatus}{1}{On orders from Santiago, head of the counterintelligence agency, find some suspicious people. Nothing specific is known except that these people appeared in town recently.}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagaFindSpyStatus}{2}{Dorothy reported strange radio traffic. The signal source is somewhere in the NCR. The transmission begins every day at 01:00 or a little later on radio channel 17.}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagaFindSpyStatus}{3}{Find whoever uses radio channel 17 every night at 01:00. Try not to let the suspects notice you.}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagaFindSpyStatus}{17}{You found out who is conducting the mysterious radio traffic. It's Smith. You need to hear the conversation to the end.}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagaFindSpyStatus}{18}{Smith noticed you watching him. You couldn't hear the transmission to the end.}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagaFindSpyStatus}{19}{You didn't hear the transmission to the end, but it's clear that Smith is the one Santiago is after.}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagaFindSpyStatus}{20}{Bishop's spy turned out to be a man named Smith. You must urgently report to Santiago that an assassination is being prepared against Councilor Westin.}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagaFindSpyStatus}{21}{Task complete. The spy turned out to be Smith.}

{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagaFindSpyStatus}{QName}{NCR}
{CritterProperty::NcrSantiagaFindSpyStatus}{QDesc}{Find the spy for Santiago}
#==================================================================================================#
