{CritterProperty::NCRFelixSaveBrahmin}{1}{One of the brahmin on Westin's ranch has been poisoned by something. Check what happened to the animal. If you can cure the brahmin, return to Felix.}
{CritterProperty::NCRFelixSaveBrahmin}{2}{Fighting back your disgust, you "extracted" from the brahmin the filth it had eaten. Return to Felix for your reward.}
{CritterProperty::NCRFelixSaveBrahmin}{3}{You saved the brahmin's life! That's what matters, right? And it doesn't matter how you had to do it.}

{CritterProperty::NCRFelixSaveBrahmin}{QName}{NCR}
