{CritterProperty::NCRFelixFindBrahmin}{2}{You caught a brahmin. Return to Felix. Try not to let the brahmin fall behind.}
{CritterProperty::NCRFelixFindBrahmin}{3}{You brought the brahmin to Felix.}

