{CritterProperty::NCRHubBook}{QDesc}{Hub Bibliography}
#==================================================================================================#
# Бракованная партия винтовок.
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{1}{Caravan master Dappo sent an angry letter to the weapons dealer Buster. Buster asks you to find out what's going on.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{2}{Dappo believes Buster sold him defective weapons. You need to return to the dealer.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{3}{You settled the conflict between Buster and Dappo by paying the caravan master a sum that compensated the losses from the lost caravan.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{4}{You exposed Buster. It seems he sold the caravan master a batch of defective weapons.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{5}{You got the money from Buster. You need to pay it to Dappo as compensation for the losses he suffered when the caravan was lost.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{6}{You paid Dappo. He's ready to work with Buster again.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{7}{You reconciled the two traders the simplest way - by paying Dappo compensation. Not a bad outcome.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{9}{Even though Buster never confessed, you're certain: Buster sometimes supplies caravan masters with defective weapons. This time you helped settle the dispute with Dappo.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{10}{You need to find the guards of the caravan that the raiders robbed.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{11}{Talk to the caravan guards. You can find them at the NCR Bazaar, in Mike's joint.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{12}{One of the caravan guards, Jim, vanished from the NCR right after the caravan returned home. Find Jim - his behavior may be connected to the incident.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{13}{You found out why the caravan guards' weapons failed. One of the caravan drivers, a junkie, swapped the live ammo for blanks. Return to Dappo.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{14}{You told Dappo about Jim's trick. You can return to Buster.}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{15}{You found out what happened to Dappo's caravan during the raider attack. Next time Dappo will be more careful about hiring guards for his shipments.}

{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{QName}{NCR}
{CritterProperty::NcrBusterBrokenrifles}{QDesc}{Trouble with the Guns}
