{CritterProperty::ReddWadeCaravanEscort}{3}{You attacked Ben Wade's caravan traveling from Redding to Vault City. Wade will probably never hire you to guard his shipments.}
{CritterProperty::ReddWadeCaravanEscort}{4}{Failure: You abandoned Ben Wade's caravan in the Wasteland. You won't get a reward.}
