{CritterProperty::ReddWadeCaravanEscort}{7}{You killed the guide of the Redding - Vault City caravan. Ben Wade is unlikely to want to deal with you.}
{CritterProperty::ReddWadeCaravanEscort}{8}{Excellent! The caravan safely reached its destination. Collect your pay from Ben Wade.}
{CritterProperty::ReddWadeCaravanEscort}{9}{You are with the caravan. Try to keep the cargo safe and protect the guide throughout the route.}
