# Зачистка трюмов. Сан-Франциско
{CritterProperty::SFRonKillBeasts}{1}{At the request of Captain Ron Myers, kill all the inhabitants of the tanker's lower decks, alone or as part of a group. You personally must finish off at least one creature from this whole menagerie, or the captain will not appreciate your help.}
{CritterProperty::SFRonKillBeasts}{2}{You personally killed one of the terrible monsters living in the tanker's holds. The rest still need to be destroyed.}
{CritterProperty::SFRonKillBeasts}{3}{You cleared the tanker's holds of monsters of every kind.}
{CritterProperty::SFRonKillBeasts}{4}{You helped the tanker captain deal with the monsters in the holds.}

{CritterProperty::SFRonKillBeasts}{QName}{San Francisco}
{CritterProperty::SFRonKillBeasts}{QDesc}{Clearing the holds.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Пропавшие панки. Сан-Франциско
{CritterProperty::SFRonFindbodies}{1}{At Captain Myers' request, go down to the tanker's lower decks and find four of his crew members, alive or dead. Note: to determine the cause of the punks' deaths, use the "Science" skill.}
{CritterProperty::SFRonFindbodies}{2}{The first of the missing crew members has been found. Dead, as was to be expected.}
{CritterProperty::SFRonFindbodies}{3}{The second has been found... There are no bullet wounds on the body, only marks of numerous bites and torn flesh. The local monsters finished off this poor wretch.}
{CritterProperty::SFRonFindbodies}{4}{Another body. This man was probably attacked by a centaur. He died from numerous wounds and radiation.}
{CritterProperty::SFRonFindbodies}{5}{The last of the missing punks has been found. They are all dead. The captain must be told.}
{CritterProperty::SFRonFindbodies}{6}{Unfortunately, all the crew members missing on the lower decks were found dead...}

{CritterProperty::SFRonFindbodies}{QName}{San Francisco}
{CritterProperty::SFRonFindbodies}{QDesc}{Clearing the holds.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Возрождение Императора. Сан-Франциско
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{1}{The hard drives of the Shi Emperor (that is what they call their supercomputer) were formatted by an unknown person. Councilor Ken Lee promises to pay well for restoring the Emperor's data.}
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{2}{You were unable to restore the Emperor's memory.}
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{3}{You managed to restore 1% of the data on the Emperor's hard drive.}
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{4}{You managed to restore 2% of the data on the Emperor's hard drive.}
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{5}{You managed to restore 3% of the data on the Emperor's hard drive.}
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{6}{You managed to restore 1% of the data on the Emperor's hard drive. The data is fully restored!}
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{7}{You managed to restore 2% of the data on the Emperor's hard drive. The data is fully restored!}
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{8}{You managed to restore 3% of the data on the Emperor's hard drive. The data is fully restored!}
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{9}{On behalf of the Shi people, Councilor Ken Lee thanked you for restoring the data on the Emperor's hard drives.}
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{10}{You failed the task.}

{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{QName}{San Francisco}
{CritterProperty::SFKenliImperatorRestore}{QDesc}{Revival of the Emperor}
#==================================================================================================#
# Формат: С. Сан-Франциско
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7ImperatorFormat}{1}{On orders from AHS-7 in San Francisco, format the hard drives of the Shi Emperor.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7ImperatorFormat}{2}{Mission failed. Perhaps you should return to this task later, when you are more experienced.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7ImperatorFormat}{3}{Formatting complete. Data destroyed in the Shi Emperor's memory: 1%.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7ImperatorFormat}{4}{Formatting complete. Data destroyed in the Shi Emperor's memory: 3%.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7ImperatorFormat}{5}{Formatting complete. Data destroyed in the Shi Emperor's memory: 5%.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7ImperatorFormat}{6}{You completed AHS-7's task. The data in the Shi Emperor's memory has been destroyed.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7ImperatorFormat}{7}{You failed to complete the Hubologists' task.}

{CritterProperty::SFAhs7ImperatorFormat}{QName}{San Francisco}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7ImperatorFormat}{QDesc}{Format: C.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Нэнси и Сид. Сан-Франциско  
{CritterProperty::SFSlimSidnancy}{1}{Slim, the bartender from the tanker, asks you to find the punks Nancy and Sid, who vanished without a trace.}
{CritterProperty::SFSlimSidnancy}{2}{Find the drug dealers' shack on the coast near San Francisco. Nancy should be there. She will tell you where Sid is and what happened to them.}
{CritterProperty::SFSlimSidnancy}{3}{You found the drug dealers' shack. Unfortunately, you came too late; Nancy died from blood loss. By the time you found the tent, the girl was already dead. Sid has vanished.}
{CritterProperty::SFSlimSidnancy}{4}{You told Slim that you could not find Sid. Nancy is dead. By all signs, it was her boyfriend who finished her off.}
{CritterProperty::SFSlimSidnancy}{5}{Nancy is dead. She was most likely stabbed by one of the drug dealers whose tent you found on the coast near San Francisco.}
{CritterProperty::SFSlimSidnancy}{6}{Apparently Nancy took her own life after overdosing on Jet. Sid disappeared without a trace.}

{CritterProperty::SFSlimSidnancy}{QName}{San Francisco}
{CritterProperty::SFSlimSidnancy}{QDesc}{Nancy and Sid}
#==================================================================================================#
# AHS - 7, Сан-Франциско. Сюжетная линия, побочный квест.
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Invitations}{1}{Convince three residents of the Atoll of the need to undergo replication. Then return to San Francisco.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Invitations}{2}{You successfully won over one of the Atoll workers. He promised to stop by the replication center. Two more still need to be worked on.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Invitations}{3}{The second one agreed. Only the last holdout remains.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Invitations}{4}{Three from the Atoll platform agreed to visit the Hubologist center and undergo replication. The task is complete. Return to AHS-7.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Invitations}{5}{You passed the test and have been accepted into the Hubologists. Three from the Atoll underwent replication.}

{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Invitations}{QName}{San Francisco}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Invitations}{QDesc}{Introduction to Hubology.}
#==================================================================================================#
# СФ. АХС-7. Правосудие Хаба.Квест для доступа к сюжетной линии
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7HubJudgement}{1}{To prove your faith, destroy those who have renounced the blessings of the Church of Hubology.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7HubJudgement}{2}{You decided to let the poor wretches flee. Mercy can kill too, but not in this case.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7HubJudgement}{3}{Ingvar's family got away safely. No one will be able to find them if they followed your advice.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7HubJudgement}{4}{Hubologist justice in action. They look harmless, but we know the treachery of these traitors knows no bounds.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7HubJudgement}{5}{The task is complete. All members of Ingvar's family are dead.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7HubJudgement}{6}{You failed to live up to the Hub's trust and did not complete the task. Ingvar's family survived, but you are no longer a member of the Church.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7HubJudgement}{7}{Your faith is enviable. A brilliantly executed assignment, and now you are already AHS-3.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7HubJudgement}{8}{You saved Ingvar's family, yet managed to deceive the shrewd Hubologist.}

{CritterProperty::SFAhs7HubJudgement}{QName}{San Francisco}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7HubJudgement}{QDesc}{The Hub's Justice.}
#==================================================================================================#
# СФ. АХС-7. Телохранитель для брата Хономера. Квест для доступа к сюжетной линии
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Escort}{1}{You have been entrusted with an important mission. Find the Hubologist Hofnomer and follow his instructions.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Escort}{2}{You must escort Hofnomer to the Hubologist base in the Wasteland, south of San Francisco. Protect the Hubologist from attacks.}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Escort}{3}{You have completed the AHS-7 mission and escorted Hofnomer to the Hubologist base.}

{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Escort}{QName}{San Francisco}
{CritterProperty::SFAhs7Escort}{QDesc}{Bodyguard for Brother Hofnomer.}
#==================================================================================================#
# СФ купить рецепт хитиновой брони у доктора Тиганга
{CritterProperty::SFTigangRecipe}{1}{Jing T. Gang sells the technology for crafting unique chitin armor.}
{CritterProperty::SFTigangRecipe}{2}{You have bought the recipe for chitin armor.}

{CritterProperty::SFTigangRecipe}{QName}{San Francisco}
{CritterProperty::SFTigangRecipe}{QDesc}{{Chitin Armor.}
#==================================================================================================#
#================================ Станция репликации №4 ===========================================#
#==================================================================================================#
# Взорвать репликатор на станции репликации №4.
{CritterProperty::GEReplExplodeTank}{1}{Blow up the replication tank that has malfunctioned.}
{CritterProperty::GEReplExplodeTank}{2}{The explosives are set. Get the hell out of here before the plastic explosive blows everything to pieces!}
{CritterProperty::GEReplExplodeTank}{3}{You blew up one of the replication tanks that produce hordes of crazed ghouls. Collect your reward from the trader at any replication station.}
{CritterProperty::GEReplExplodeTank}{4}{You helped Captain Smollett blow up the faulty replicator.}

{CritterProperty::GEReplExplodeTank}{QName}{Replication Station No.4}
{CritterProperty::GEReplExplodeTank}{QDesc}{Hot reset.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Поговорить с капитаном Смоллетом на поверхности у станции репликации №4
{CritterProperty::GEReplFindstation}{1}{Find the leader of the Hubologist strike team on the surface of Replication Station No.4.}
{CritterProperty::GEReplFindstation}{2}{You agreed to help the Hubologists deal with the malfunctioning machinery at the replication station and solve the ghoul problem.}

{CritterProperty::GEReplFindstation}{QName}{Replication Station No.4}
{CritterProperty::GEReplFindstation}{QDesc}{Emergency situation.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Убить 5 гулей так, чтобы они больше не поднялись
{CritterProperty::GEReplNopasaran}{1}{Kill five replicated ghouls at Replication Station No.4.}
{CritterProperty::GEReplNopasaran}{2}{1 replicated ghoul killed.}
{CritterProperty::GEReplNopasaran}{3}{2 replicated ghouls killed.}
{CritterProperty::GEReplNopasaran}{4}{3 replicated ghouls killed.}
{CritterProperty::GEReplNopasaran}{5}{4 replicated ghouls killed.}
{CritterProperty::GEReplNopasaran}{6}{5 replicated ghouls killed. See the Hubologist trader at any replication station to collect your reward.}
{CritterProperty::GEReplNopasaran}{7}{You completed the task for the scientist at Replication Station No.4. There are now 5 fewer crazed ghouls in the Wasteland.}

{CritterProperty::GEReplNopasaran}{QName}{Replication Station No.4}
{CritterProperty::GEReplNopasaran}{QDesc}{No pasaran!}
#==================================================================================================#
#================================ Поиск заброшенного склада =======================================#
#==================================================================================================#
# Quest to locate an abandoned military depot.
{CritterProperty::QWarehouse}{1}{Locate an abandoned military depot.}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouse}{2}{You have found an abandoned military depot location.}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouse}{3}{You have found an abandoned military depot. You've told Old Man about this.}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouse}{4}{You've failed to find the location of an abandoned military depot.}

{CritterProperty::QWarehouse}{QName}{Abandoned military depot's location}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouse}{QDesc}{Locate abandoned military depot.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Quest to locate an abandoned military depot. Sub-quest 1.
{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub1}{1}{Old Man asked you to find and bring back his daughter, she's somewhere in Den, in a junkies commune.}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub1}{2}{Old Man’s daughter asked you to find her beloved one. The guy’s probable name is Max.}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub1}{3}{Pass daughter's message to her father.}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub1}{4}{Completed. The military depot is now marked on the map.}

{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub1}{QName}{Abandoned military depot's location}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub1}{QDesc}{Find the military depot location. Old Man will let you know it after you find his daughter.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Quest to locate an abandoned military depot. Sub-quest 2.
{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub2}{1}{Player's last job place is Golden Globos Porn.}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub2}{2}{You need to find a pretty girl for the new movie.}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub2}{3}{Find Player, trick him into giving you the key card.}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub2}{4}{Completed. You’ve found the key to military depot.}

{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub2}{QName}{Abandoned military depot's location}
{CritterProperty::QWarehouseSub2}{QDesc}{Find a key card to the military depot entrance. Obtain it from former Old Man's partner, Player, in New-Reno.}
#==================================================================================================#
#============================ Лучший охотник Пустоши ==============================================#
#==================================================================================================#
# Квест 1. Убить 10 кротокрысов, затем поговорить со Смайли, после этого принести осколочную гранату на БГ.
{CritterProperty::BarterLourensRats1}{1}{On Hughes and Lawrence's orders, find a molerat nest in the wasteland and bring the hunters a molerat egg. Kill female molerats; one of them may have an egg.}
{CritterProperty::BarterLourensRats1}{2}{Hughes and Lawrence apparently got something wrong. You've already killed a dozen molerats, but never found an egg. Maybe you should find another experienced trapper and ask for advice.}
{CritterProperty::BarterLourensRats1}{3}{Smiley thinks you've been pranked. Find a fragmentation grenade and give it to Lawrence disguised as a molerat egg.}
{CritterProperty::BarterLourensRats1}{4}{You have earned the respect of the hunters in Modoc.}

{CritterProperty::BarterLourensRats1}{QName}{Best Hunter of the Wasteland}
{CritterProperty::BarterLourensRats1}{QDesc}{Bring a molerat egg to Hughes and Lawrence.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Квест 2. Использовать флейту на 5 крыс и принести их Лоуренсу в Модок.
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsFlute}{1}{Use the ultrasonic hypnotizer obtained from Hughes and Lawrence on five rats in the Wasteland.}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsFlute}{2}{The hypnotizer has been tested on 5 rats in the Wasteland. Return to Hughes and Lawrence with a report and bring 5 paralyzed rats.}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsFlute}{3}{You helped Lawrence and Hughes test the ultrasonic hypnotizer on 5 rats in the Wasteland.}

{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsFlute}{QName}{Best Hunter of the Wasteland}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsFlute}{QDesc}{Dance to my tune.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Квест 2. Использовать токсичную крысу на флоатера. Многоразовый
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceFloater}{1}{Use Hughes and Lawrence's supertoxin on a paralyzed rat. Then throw the toxic rat into a floater's maw. }
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceFloater}{2}{You tested the supertoxin on a floater from the Wasteland. The desired effect was not achieved. Report the failure to Lawrence in Modoc.}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceFloater}{3}{The supertoxin that Lawrence and Hughes had such high hopes for didn't work on the floater. You can continue the tests, but it's doubtful they'll yield a positive result.}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceFloater}{4}{Another syringe of supertoxin. Another rat. Another floater. The poison didn't work again. Report the failure to Hughes.}

{CritterProperty::ModLourenceFloater}{QName}{Best Hunter of the Wasteland}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceFloater}{QDesc}{Breakfast for the Floater.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Квест 3. Зачистить локацию с кротокрысами
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsColony}{1}{The coordinates of the runaway EM-22's lair full of molerats are recorded in your Pip-Boy. Find the special mark on the ground in front of the cave entrance and use Lawrence's ointment to lure the animals to the surface.}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsColony}{2}{You failed to destroy the colony of intelligent molerats in time.}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsColony}{3}{You destroyed all the molerats, but never found the Empirical Bear. Maybe it managed to escape. Return to the hunters in Modoc.}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsColony}{4}{You used Lawrence's bait. Now all that's left is to wait for it to work.}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsColony}{5}{You destroyed the colony of intelligent molerats on Hughes and Lawrence's orders.}

{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsColony}{QName}{Best Hunter of the Wasteland}
{CritterProperty::ModLourenceRatsColony}{QDesc}{Colony of intelligent molerats.}
#==================================================================================================#
#=========================================== Наварро ==============================================#
#==================================================================================================#
# Считать данные с блоков памяти роботов Сьерры. Наварро
{CritterProperty::NavSoftJob}{1}{Collect statistical data from the memory blocks of the Sierra combat robots. Once the scanner's collected data reaches 100%, return to Henry in Navarro.}
{CritterProperty::NavSoftJob}{2}{You completed Henry's task and returned the scanner.}

{CritterProperty::NavSoftJob}{QName}{Navarro}
{CritterProperty::NavSoftJob}{QDesc}{Easy work.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Убить 5 роботов с помощью импульсных ракет
{CritterProperty::NavHenryEmpTest}{1}{On Professor Henry's orders, hit 5 different robots with EMP rockets. Then return to Navarro. Progress: 0 of 5 robots.}
{CritterProperty::NavHenryEmpTest}{2}{On Professor Henry's orders, hit 5 different robots with EMP rockets. Then return to Navarro. Progress: 1 of 5 robots.}
{CritterProperty::NavHenryEmpTest}{3}{On Professor Henry's orders, hit 5 different robots with EMP rockets. Then return to Navarro. Progress: 2 of 5 robots.}
{CritterProperty::NavHenryEmpTest}{4}{On Professor Henry's orders, hit 5 different robots with EMP rockets. Then return to Navarro. Progress: 3 of 5 robots.}
{CritterProperty::NavHenryEmpTest}{5}{On Professor Henry's orders, hit 5 different robots with EMP rockets. Then return to Navarro. Progress: 4 of 5 robots.}
{CritterProperty::NavHenryEmpTest}{6}{On Professor Henry's orders, hit 5 different robots with EMP rockets. Then return to Navarro. Progress: 5 of 5 robots.}
{CritterProperty::NavHenryEmpTest}{7}{You completed Henry's task and field-tested a working prototype of the EMP rocket.}

{CritterProperty::NavHenryEmpTest}{QName}{Navarro}
{CritterProperty::NavHenryEmpTest}{QDesc}{Field testing.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Принести профессору Генри в Наварро: 10 бронебойных ракет, 5 импульсных гранат и 20 микросхем
{CritterProperty::NavHenryProtoMaterials}{1}{Bring Professor Henry in Navarro 10 armor-piercing rockets, 5 pulse grenades, and 20 microchips. The scientist needs the materials to develop a prototype of a new kind of ammunition.}
{CritterProperty::NavHenryProtoMaterials}{2}{You fulfilled Professor Henry's request and supplied the test material for developing a prototype of a new kind of rocket.}

{CritterProperty::NavHenryProtoMaterials}{QName}{Navarro}
{CritterProperty::NavHenryProtoMaterials}{QDesc}{Prototype.}
