# Manota's quest for jewelry, Primitive Tribe.
{CritterProperty::TribManotaNecklace}{1}{Find a precious necklace for Manota.}
{CritterProperty::TribManotaNecklace}{2}{You refused to look for a necklace for Manota.}
{CritterProperty::TribManotaNecklace}{3}{You got the necklace for Manota.}

{CritterProperty::TribManotaNecklace}{QName}{Primal Tribe}
{CritterProperty::TribManotaNecklace}{QDesc}{Find a necklace for Manota.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Help Sulik find some items for tribe, Primitive Tribe.
{CritterProperty::TribSulikStuff}{1}{Primal Tribe needs several gecko pelts and a couple of antidotes.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikStuff}{2}{You refused to help the tribe.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikStuff}{3}{You brought the items to Sulik.}

{CritterProperty::TribSulikStuff}{QName}{Primal Tribe.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikStuff}{QDesc}{Find gecko pelts and antidote for Sulik.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Find 3 healing powders for Gojatlah the shaman, Primitive Tribe. 
{CritterProperty::TribShamanPowder}{1}{Shaman needs 3 healing powders for his ritual.}
{CritterProperty::TribShamanPowder}{2}{You refused to help the shaman.}
{CritterProperty::TribShamanPowder}{3}{You brought the healing powders to Gojatlah.}

{CritterProperty::TribShamanPowder}{QName}{Primal Tribe}
{CritterProperty::TribShamanPowder}{QDesc}{Bring healing powders to Gojatlah.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Bring big book of science to Mayara.
{CritterProperty::TribMaiaraBook}{1}{Mayara, Keeper of wisdom, is looking for a big book of science. Bring it to her.}
{CritterProperty::TribMaiaraBook}{2}{You refused to help Mayara. Your reputation within the tribe is lowered.}
{CritterProperty::TribMaiaraBook}{3}{Mayara gladly accepted your book and shared her wisdom with you.}

{CritterProperty::TribMaiaraBook}{QName}{Primal Tribe}
{CritterProperty::TribMaiaraBook}{QDesc}{Mayara's new wisdom, big book of science.}
