# Dick-measuring contest with tribe's toughest warrior, Primitive Tribe. 
{CritterProperty::TribMuscoTest}{1}{Find a way to defeat the tribe's toughest warrior, Motelchiuh.}
{CritterProperty::TribMuscoTest}{2}{Being grateful for your help, Mayara told you a secret to defeat Motelchiuh.}
{CritterProperty::TribMuscoTest}{3}{You have used your wits to defeat the tribe's toughest warrior.}

{CritterProperty::TribMuscoTest}{QName}{Primal Tribe}
{CritterProperty::TribMuscoTest}{QDesc}{Defeat Motelchiuh.}
#==================================================================================================#
# Protect the Primitive tribe.
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{1}{Raiders are preparing to attack! Hurry up!}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{2}{You have helped the tribe in destroying the raiders.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{3}{Mission failed. You ran away from the battlefield.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{4}{Mission failed. You got killed.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{5}{Mission failed. Tribe drove off raiders without your help.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{6}{You helped the tribe to defend against raiders' attack.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{7}{You have earned the tribe's respect.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{8}{Mission failed. You were late.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{9}{Mission failed. Raiders have left.}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{10}{Raiders are attacking the tribe, hepl them!}

{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{QName}{Primal Tribe}
{CritterProperty::TribSulikRaid}{QDesc}{Help the tribe, they are under raider attack!}
