# Квест "Добыть самку", Убежище 13
{CritterProperty::V13Dclaw}{1}{The sergeant at the vault entrance gave your group the task of tracking down and bringing him a live female deathclaw. (To do this, you first need to knock her unconscious and put a special muzzle on her, then she will be docile and follow you.)}
{CritterProperty::V13Dclaw}{2}{You have captured the female deathclaw. Now it's important to deliver her to the vault in one piece.}
{CritterProperty::V13Dclaw}{3}{You failed to deliver the female deathclaw and lost the muzzle. You need to talk to the sergeant; maybe he'll give you another one.}
