{CritterProperty::V13DclawEggs}{2}{Completed. You delivered the intelligent Deathclaw egg to the Professor.}
{CritterProperty::V13DclawEggs}{3}{Completed. You delivered the egg and convinced the Professor to raise and bring up an intelligent Deathclaw.}
{CritterProperty::V13DclawEggs}{4}{Failed. You refused to help Goris.}
