# Припугнуть Вейстина		# 4220	
{4220001}{}{Smith, whom you recently met, has some kind of personal score to settle with Westin. He asks you to help him "visit" the councilman. The whole thing looks very suspicious.}
{4220002}{}{You agreed to help Smith sneak into councilman Westin's ranch. You need to meet Smith near the Ranch gate. Smith won't wait long, so don't be late!}
{4220003}{}{You safely distracted the guard at the entrance, and Smith slipped onto the Ranch grounds. What he'll be doing in there, only God knows. Wait for his return at Dusty's bar.}
{4220004}{}{Smith "scared" Westin with your help. Who could care what became of the councilman?}
{4220005}{}{You told the sheriff about Smith's plans. Dumont promised to take measures, but for some reason it seems to you that he didn't quite believe you.}

{4220101}{}{NCR}
{4220102}{}{"Scare" Westin.}
