# СЮЖЕТ						# 5000
{5000001}{}{Take Martin's advice and undergo the replication procedure.}
{5000002}{}{The Chosen One... That name thundered across all the Wasteland. According to Martin, the Chosen One vanished without a trace some time ago. Martin needs any information you can find.}
{5000003}{}{You spoke with Johnson from Redding. He met the Chosen One shortly before his disappearance. A replication chip, removed by a doctor from a replicant, caught the Chosen One's interest. He immediately decided to find out what the Hubologists use this microchip for.}
{5000004}{}{You broke into the secret Hubologist laboratory and studied the materials with the help of a supercomputer. The Chosen One was right: the replication chips have a second purpose, unrelated to reviving a replicant. The network of mysterious laboratories is somehow connected to this unknown function of the replication chip.}

{5000101}{}{Search for the Chosen One}
{5000102}{}{Mysterious disappearance.}
